---
title: Carb Smart Jalapeño-Double Beef Chili with Cheddar Cheese
description: This nourishing low-carb chili swaps out traditional beans for lots of wholesome veggies! Spicy jalapeños and melty cheddar cheese amp up the deliciousness.

